data.description: One story custom home with 4 bed, 3 bath, 3 car garage and pool. Features open floorplan, large living area with stone fireplace & ceiling treatment. Kitchen features large island with tons of cabinets. Master has large closet, linen closet & separate jetted tub & shower. Property also has 14 x 60 RV pad with electricity. Updates include fresh paint throughout house, HVAC system and ventilation, pool pump, updated lvp flooring in master, living, dining, and one bedroom.
